The home boasts four spacious bedrooms, each with its own unique character. The master suite is a tranquil retreat with a private en-suite bathroom. The home is a true testament to the elegance and craftsmanship of a bygone era. The home exudes historic charm while offering the modern comforts and conveniences of today's lifestyle.
